Ducking volume change is indistinguishable but is there you will notice that when riffers are speaking default audio is gone hence the subs being turned on by default so that words aren't missing. If your subtitle is off or the character set is wrong simply add the edited sub with the same name but number it 28. Icons have been supplied by me and MovieIconMan thank you for the Icons sir.
